You have exceeded your premium request allowance. We have automatically switched you to GPT-4.1 which is included with your plan. [Enable additional paid premium requests](command:chat.enablePremiumOverages) to continue using premium models.```seqdiag
actor User
boundary ProductPage
control ProductController
participant ":ProductService" as ProductService
participant ":ProductModel" as ProductModel
database Database

User->ProductPage: 1. Select filter options (keyword, category, price)
activate ProductPage
activate User

ProductPage->ProductController: 2. GET /products/filter?keyword=&categoryId=&price=
activate ProductController

ProductController->ProductService: 5. filterProducts(params)
activate ProductService

ProductService->ProductModel: 6. Build filter criteria
activate ProductModel

ProductModel->Database: 7. Retrieve filtered product data
activate Database
Database-->ProductModel: 8. Result set
deactivate Database

ProductModel-->ProductService: 9. Return filtered list + paging info
deactivate ProductModel

alt No products match
    ProductService-->ProductController: 10.1. Return empty result
    ProductController-->ProductPage: 10.1.1. Return 200 OK + empty list/message
    ProductPage-->User: 10.1.2. Show "No products found" + keep filters
else Products match
    ProductService-->ProductController: 10.2. Return FilterProductResponse
    deactivate ProductService
    ProductController-->ProductPage: 10.2.1. Return 200 OK + filtered products data
    deactivate ProductController


ProductPage-->User: 10.2.2. Display filter result
end
deactivate ProductPage
deactivate User
```